{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782925744874,"sessionID":"ses_0e161ba06ffe4N4jFh0zF4Zwuf","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_4495e600f587408fbba03166","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Convergence Report: glm-max Lineage\n\n**Stop reason:** `maxIterationsReached` (config.maxIterations=2, stopPolicy=max-iterations)\n**Total iterations:** 2\n**Questions answered:** 4/4 (100%)\n**Stop policy:** max-iterations (convergence treated as telemetry only per task instructions)\n\n## Iteration Summary\n\n| Run | Focus | newInfoRatio | Status | Key Output |\n|-----|-------|-------------|--------|------------|\n| 1 | SDK session-state + mechanical loop-like definition | 1.0 | complete | Q1+Q2 answered: 2 proven state mechanisms; N≥3 threshold |\n| 2 | Dispatch path grounding + phase 012 evidence + design options | 0.85 | complete | Q3+Q4 answered; 2 concrete design options with trade-offs |\n\n## newInfoRatio Trend\n\n- Iteration 1: 1.0 (all findings new to packet)\n- Iteration 2: 0.85 (design options new; evidence builds on iter 1)\n\n## Design Options Produced\n\n1. **Option A**: Session-scoped in-process dispatch counter (~40 lines, MEDIUM false-positive risk)\n2. **Option B**: External state file + iteration-aware counting (~80 lines, LOW false-positive risk)\n3. **Option C**: Telemetry-first rollout (supplementary to A or B)\n\n## Recommendation\n\nOption B with Option C rollout, threshold N≥3 non-command-driven dispatches per executor per session.\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/016-mk-deep-loop-guard-hardening/research/lineages/glm-max/convergence-report.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/016-mk-deep-loop-guard-hardening/research/lineages/glm-max/convergence-report.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/016-mk-deep-loop-guard-hardening/research/lineages/glm-max/convergence-report.md","time":{"start":1782925744871,"end":1782925744873}},"id":"prt_f1ea7dae6001Yve4c0cPyIx4r3","sessionID":"ses_0e161ba06ffe4N4jFh0zF4Zwuf","messageID":"msg_f1ea7b4ed001AZeTPGRQeaIciC"}}
